Cattle Feed Solutions

Premium nutrition solutions for dairy cows, beef cattle, calves, and heifers. Our scientifically formulated feeds ensure optimal health, growth, and productivity.

Cattle Feed Product Catalogue

Complete nutrition solutions for every stage of cattle development

Premium

Calf Starter 20

Fine mash/crumble, 20 % crude protein (CP) with digestible fibre, vitamins A-E and a coccidiostat; jump-starts rumen development in calves ≤ 12 weeks.

Premium

Heifer Grow 16

16 % CP developer pellet balanced for steady skeletal growth without excess fat in replacement heifers (3–15 months).

Premium

Dairy Boost 18

High-energy 18 % CP lactation ration (pellet or mash) with bypass protein, yeast culture and protected fat to support peak milk yield.

Premium

Close-Up Transition

Negative-DCAD, low-calcium mix fed 21 days pre-calving to reduce milk fever risk and ease metabolic transition.

Premium

Beef Finisher 14

14 % CP high-grain TMR concentrate that maximises daily gain and marbling in the last 90 days before slaughter.

Premium

Fiber Guard Roughage Plus

Chopped, ammoniated straw cube fortified with minerals—keeps rumen pH stable when pastures are short or lush.

Premium

Energy Mol Block 40

Self-fed molasses-urea tub (≈40 % sugar) supplying extra energy and non-protein nitrogen on dry forage.

Premium

Protein Plus 46

46 % CP soybean-meal pellet added at 1–2 kg/day to low-protein forages for growth or lactation.

Premium

Mineral Max Brick

Weatherproof salt block with Ca, P, Mg and chelated trace minerals (Zn, Cu, Se) for grazing cattle.

Premium

Silage Mate CornPak

Fermented whole-plant corn (~35 % DM) chopped and bag-sealed; economical basal energy source for all classes.
